      "text": "354o\n\nThis is more complete than I realized. see note p354Q. Type A - the more priorative psyche, right hemisphere - may be what I had been at least since 1970 when Nancy left me - i.e. beginning with my \"mescaline trip\" which was not a mescaline trip but schizophrenic psychosis in which my right hemisphere took over, & ruled until 2-74 when my left came back on & (it being rational) \"invaded the irrational\" as I put it in \"Valis.\" But Ditheon resulted, but it was not A invading B but B invading",
